    "image-with-text-1": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "disabled": false,
      "settings": {
        "image_position": "right",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "content_vertical_alignment": "center",
        "two_images_layout": "double_horizontal",
        "first_desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/image_2.png",
        "heading": "PREMIUM MARBLE BOWLS",
        "subheading": "Our Marble Bowls: A Timeless Design for Your Home and Cat",
        "text_content": "<p>The SVELDA marble bowl is more than an object; it is an invitation to live beautifully. Each piece is a harmonious blend of form and function, designed to elevate your home while celebrating the daily life you share with your companion.</p><p>Meticulously crafted from natural <strong>marble</strong> and <strong>travertine</strong>, our bowls are a testament to the enduring beauty of the earth. We use a food-safe polish wax to enhance the stone's natural elegance and protect your pet. The subtle variations in veining and tone ensure that no two bowls are exactly alike.</p><p>Yours will be a one-of-a-kind piece, just like your cat.</p><h6><strong>A Collection That Adapts to Your Style</strong></h6><p></p><p>With a clean, minimalist design, our bowls seamlessly integrate into any modern or classic interior. Choose from our distinct bowl shapes and pair them with a selection of bases: warm, natural <strong>solid wood</strong> or sleek, polished <strong>metal</strong>.</p><p>This is not just a feeding bowl. It's an essential part of your home’s aesthetic, designed for a beautiful life, together.</p>",
        "button_label": "Explore Bowls",
        "button_aria_label": "Explore Premium Bowls",
        "button_url": "shopify://collections/eat",
        "button_style": "secondary-border",
        "container_width": "inherit",
        "offset_top_desktop": 0,
        "offset_bottom_desktop": 80,
        "offset_top_mobile": 0,
        "offset_bottom_mobile": 40
      }
    },
    "image-with-text-2": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "disabled": false,
      "settings": {
        "image_position": "left",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "content_vertical_alignment": "center",
        "two_images_layout": "double_vertical",
        "first_desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/image_3_copy.png",
        "heading": "PURE WOOL MATS",
        "subheading": "Designed to Belong: A Perfect Union of Comfort and Home Decor",
        "text_content": "<p>The life you share with your pet is one of harmony. Our beds are designed to reflect this, providing a perfect union of your pet's comfort and your home's design. Meticulously crafted <strong>in Italy</strong>, we’ve sourced materials that not only feel incredible but also look impeccable, including a variety of <strong>wools</strong>, <strong>cashmere</strong>, and durable <strong>cotton</strong>. The result is a collection of beds and mats that are both a luxurious retreat for your companion and a natural, sophisticated element of your living space. With thoughtful details and an emphasis on timeless style, our beds are made to be treasured, because the best design is one that makes both you and your pet feel right at home.</p>",
        "button_label": "Discover Mats",
        "button_aria_label": "Discover Pure Wool Mats",
        "button_url": "shopify://collections/rest",
        "button_style": "secondary-border",
        "container_width": "inherit",
        "offset_top_desktop": 0,
        "offset_bottom_desktop": 80,
        "offset_top_mobile": 0,
        "offset_bottom_mobile": 40
      }
    },
