      "type": "image-with-text",
      "disabled": false,
      "settings": {
        "image_position": "right",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "content_vertical_alignment": "center",
        "two_images_layout": "double_vertical",
        "first_desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/image_2_copy4.png",
        "heading": "TOPINI",
        "subheading": "The SVELDA Toy Collection: An Artful Addition.",
        "text_content": "<p>A playful cat is a happy cat. </p><p>Our collection of toys—from the playful \"Topini\" mice to the charming \"Pesciolini\" fish—is a testament to this philosophy. These are not ordinary toys. We craft them from the same organic, high-quality materials as our luxurious textiles, ensuring they are not only safe and durable but also a natural fit for your elegant home. With the thoughtful detail of a matching toy included with every mat, we invite you to discover a world where every piece, no matter how small, is an expression of our commitment to quality and a celebration of the beautiful life you share.</p>",
        "button_label": "Shop Toys",
        "button_aria_label": "Shop Toys",
